I am working with an already frozen model, so when I run my android application, I get this exception:

Caused by: org.tensorflow.TensorFlowException: Op type not registered 'NonMaxSuppressionV3' in binary running on localhost. Make sure the Op and Kernel are registered in the binary running in this process.

I have checked the BUILD file and there is that op: non_max_suppression_op , I really don't know what to do.
Please tell me how I can fix it.
